OL,7,FAnn Stewart, owner of Seaside Chic,
OL,8,Fsays her profits are down by #2,100
OL,9,Fthis month, compared to May 2023,
OL,10,Fwhich has left her having "sleepless
OL,11,Fnights" over concern she will lose her
OL,12,Fbusiness.
OL,14,FShe said: "It's decimated all the
OL,15,Fbusinesses completely. There's no
OL,16,Ffootfall. There's no swimmers coming
OL,17,Fdown, who were really good customers
OL,18,Fof all of us.
