OL,3,CSeaham businesses say new parking
OL,4,Ccharges have 'taken away heartbeat' of
OL,5,Cmarina
OL,7,F"There's no dog walkers coming.
OL,8,FThere's no fishermen coming. So
OL,9,Fbasically, you're halving your
OL,10,Ftakings."
OL,12,FShe said the introduction of charges
OL,13,Fhas left her feeling ignored and
OL,14,F"angry", adding: "I'm very angry,
OL,15,Ffrustrated, not sleeping. Thinking
OL,16,FI've been here eight years. Am I going
OL,17,Fto lose my business? And I don't want
OL,18,Fto. I love it here."
