OL,7,FIn response, Durham County Council say
OL,8,Fthere are other free car parking sites
OL,9,Fin the town centre, which is close to
OL,10,Fthe harbour.
OL,12,FMark Jackson, Durham County Council's
OL,13,Fhead of transport and contract
OL,14,Fservices, said: "The new charges are
OL,15,Flimited to six locations and people
OL,16,Fcan still park for free in numerous
OL,17,Fother sites around Seaham town centre,
OL,18,Fall of which are a short distance from
OL,19,Fthe sea front.
