OL,7,F"Our teams have been working in Seaham
OL,8,Fsince the charges came in, looking out
OL,9,Ffor any parking and traffic issues
OL,10,Fwhich may arise, and will continue to
OL,11,Fmake regular visits."
OL,13,FThe new charges, introduced by Durham
OL,14,FCounty Council a month ago, are #1 for
OL,15,Fone hour and anything above one hour
OL,16,Fis #3, Monday to Sunday, between
OL,17,F8.00am to 6.00pm.
