OL,3,CSeaham businesses say new parking
OL,4,Ccharges have 'taken away heartbeat' of
OL,5,Cmarina
OL,7,FShe said: "Mental health, through the
OL,8,Froof. Staff asking everyday if their
OL,9,Fjobs are safe. My answer, 'no they're
OL,10,Fnot'. I can't lie to them, so my plan
OL,11,Fis to get through the summer, and
OL,12,Fafter the summer, no idea.
OL,14,F"It's heartbreaking. They've built
OL,15,FSeaham up so much, the amount what
OL,16,Fthey've spent on it, and then within a
OL,17,Fmonth they've just took the heartbeat
OL,18,Fout the place."
